<td tEditID="c1r1" style=" background-color:#FFFFFF; bEditID:r3st1; color:#000000; bLabel:main; font-size:12pt; font-family:arial;" aEditID="c1r1" locked="0" >
<![CDATA[<div style=""><div style=""><div style=""><font face="arial">Hi {!Contact.FirstName},</font></div><div style=""><font face="arial"><br></font></div><div style=""><font face="arial">Thank you for contacting Kingsbridge.</font></div><div style=""><font face="arial"><br></font></div><div style=""><font face="arial">As mentioned, <b>due to the Data Protection Act, I am unable to supply any details relating to another customer</b>.</font></div><div style=""><font face="arial"><br></font></div><div style=""><font face="arial">We have investigated this and unfortunately <b>we will not be able to send you any referral vouchers on this occasion</b>. <br><br>You may be able to get more information by speaking to your friend. We are happy to speak with them directly to explain the circumstances.</font></div><div style=""><font face="arial"><br></font></div><div style=""><font face="arial">Kind regards,</font></div><div style=""><font face="arial"><br></font></div><div style=""><font face="arial">{!User.FirstName}</font></div><div style=""><font face="arial">Customer Service Team</font></div><div style=""><font face="arial"><br></font></div><div style=""><font face="arial">E: customersupport@kingsbridge.co.uk</font></div><div style=""><font face="arial">T: 01242 808 740</font></div></div></div>]]></td>
</tr>
</table>